title: 이달의소녀탐구 #140 (LOONA TV #140)
summary:
Kim Lip has been shooting for a long time and the outdoor shooting is complete.
0:28 -- HaHee praises her for performing so well. Kim Lip goes on to explain how she did
her expressions so well.
0:47 -- On the way, they stop at a place where HeeJin sees a toy. It is a frog and they
think of our maknae, YeoJin.
